<HEAD>Coup Plot Uncovered By Government</HEAD>
<DATELINE>MONROVIA, Liberia (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   The government said Tuesday that 12 men
_ including an opposition party leader _ have been arrested in a
plot to overthrow the government of President Samuel Doe.
   Seven coup plotters were still at large, including an army
