here Monday night to raise money for Minnesota Attorney General
Hubert Humphrey III, a Democrat who is challenging U.S. Sen. Dave
Durenberger, R-Minn, for his seat this year. Humphrey is the son of
the late Sen. Hubert H. Humphrey Jr.
   At a private fund-raiser after his performance, Keillor said he
had worked in several political campaigns but regretted never
having worked for the late senator and vice president.
