at 9:45 p.m. at Leonard Morse Hospital. She weighed 7 pounds, 13
ounces.
   ``I'm thrilled to death,'' said Flutie, 25.
   ``When I think now how people live and die with their football
teams every Sunday, and how quarterbacks worry about their jobs
