<TEXT>
   Homosexual or bisexual males: 35,954, or 63 percent.
   Intravenous drug abusers: 10,031, or 18 percent.
   Homosexual male and drug abusers: 4,186, or 7 percent.
   Heterosexual cases: 2,254, or 4 percent.
   Transfusion or blood cases: 1,481, or 3 percent.
   Hemophilia patients: 615, or 1 percent
   Undetermined transmission cause: 1,805, or 3 percent
