   Bank of New York Co. says it is beginning a
$1.08 billion tender offer for Irving Bank Corp. after having
received approval to make the bid from the Securities and Exchange
Commission.
   SEC approval os the registration statement allows Bank of New
York to issue its prospectus, Bank of New York spokesman Owen Brady
said Monday.
